ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 13, 2022</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104xks1665702799087.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xks1665702799087.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xks1665702799087.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"xks1665702799087\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                                       \n DTD Item Name\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">This field lists the DTD items that are direct children of the tree node selected in the tree view.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xks1665702799087__p_d5726e1_d5727e1_d5728e1\">DTD items include elements representing Uniface fields or entities, their attributes, and the multiplicity operator of elements. The operator determines how many times an element is allowed to occur inside its parent element.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"xks1665702799087__table_d545e1_d546e1_d547e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">XML Multiplicity Operators</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xks1665702799087__table_d545e1_d546e1_d547e1__entry__1\">\n Operator\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xks1665702799087__table_d545e1_d546e1_d547e1__entry__2\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xks1665702799087__table_d545e1_d546e1_d547e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">*</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xks1665702799087__table_d545e1_d546e1_d547e1__entry__2\">\n The element may occur zero, once, or many times within its parent element.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xks1665702799087__table_d545e1_d546e1_d547e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">?</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xks1665702799087__table_d545e1_d546e1_d547e1__entry__2\">\n The element may occur zero or once within its parent element.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xks1665702799087__table_d545e1_d546e1_d547e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">+</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xks1665702799087__table_d545e1_d546e1_d547e1__entry__2\">\n The element may occur once or many times within its parent element.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xks1665702799087__table_d545e1_d546e1_d547e1__entry__1\">\n                     No operator\n                  </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xks1665702799087__table_d545e1_d546e1_d547e1__entry__2\">\n The element must always occur once within its parent element.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xks1665702799087__p_d5729e1_d5730e1_d5731e1\">Click the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">DTD Item Name</span> button to sort the DTD items alphabetically.</p>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8424052\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8424052\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "DTD Item Name Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 13, 2022 Summarize Uniface 10.4 DTD Item Name This field lists the DTD items that are direct children of the tree node selected in the tree view. DTD items include elements representing Uniface fields or entities, their attributes, and the multiplicity operator of elements. The operator determines how many times an element is allowed to occur inside its parent element. Table 1. XML Multiplicity Operators Operator Description * The element may occur zero, once, or many times within its parent element. ? The element may occur zero or once within its parent element. + The element may occur once or many times within its parent element. No operator The element must always occur once within its parent element. Click the DTD Item Name button to sort the DTD items alphabetically. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}